                           </note>
                        </msItem>
                        
                        <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3.9">
                           <title type="complete" xml:lang="gez">ታሪክ፡ ዝውእቱ፡ ነገረ፡ ወግ፡ አመ፡ <sic resp="PRS3562Dillmann">ተቀሐው፡</sic>
